[[魅力克利夫蘭|魅力克利夫蘭]]是一部美國[[情境喜劇|情境喜劇]]，在2010年6月16日在美國[[:en:TV_Land|:en:TV Land]]電視台首映。這部情境喜劇是TV Land首次製播的喜劇。這部戲也是該台收視率最高的劇集。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2010/06/17/hot-in-cleveland-attracts-record-ratings-for-tv-land/|title='Hot in Cleveland' attracts record ratings for TV Land|last=Rice|first=Lynette|work=''Hollywood Insider''|publisher=''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]''|date=June 17, 2010|accessdate=June 17, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619005240/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2010/06/17/hot-in-cleveland-attracts-record-ratings-for-tv-land/|archivedate=2010-06-19}}</ref>魅力克利夫蘭是由[[肖恩·海斯|肖恩·海斯]]和Hazy Mills製作，使用[[多鏡頭模式|多鏡頭]]的方式在現場觀眾前錄影，於[[:en:CBS_Studio_Center|:en:CBS Studio Center]]攝影棚拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/tv/index.ssf/2010/06/hot_in_cleveland_embraces_our.html|title='Hot in Cleveland' embraces our fair city instead of bashing it, Valerie Bertinelli says|last=Dawidziak|first=Mark|work=Cleveland.com|publisher=Cleveland Live, Inc|date=June 13, 2010|accessdate=June 18, 2010}}</ref>

